.TH btctax-tui-edit 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
btctax\-tui\-edit \- interactive editor for a btctax vault (records reconciliation decisions)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B btctax\-tui\-edit
[\fB\-\-vault\fR \fIPATH\fR | \fIPATH\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B btctax\-tui\-edit
is the interactive terminal EDITOR for a btctax vault. It shows the same tabs as the
read\-only viewer
.BR btctax\-tui (1)
and adds the full set of reconciliation actions. Every write is an append\-only event (or a
typed side\-table upsert) recorded only AFTER an explicit, payload\-showing confirmation; the
vault file itself is written only via the atomic save path.
.PP
On launch it prompts for the vault passphrase. The vault path is taken from
.B \-\-vault
.I PATH
or a bare positional
.IR PATH ;
when omitted it defaults to
.BR ~/Documents/BitcoinTax/vault.pgp .
Press
.B ?
at any time for the in\-app keymap overlay (the same bindings listed below).
.SH TABS
Holdings, Disposals, Income, Tax, Forms, Compliance \(em identical to
.BR btctax\-tui (1).
.SH KEY BINDINGS
.SS Navigation
.TP
.B Tab / Shift\-Tab
Switch tab.
.TP
.B \(<- / \(-> , h / l
Move the column cursor left / right on the Holdings, Disposals, and Income tabs.
.TP
.B s
Sort the focused column (toggles ascending / descending; a new column sorts
ascending first).
.TP
.B [ / ]
Change tax year (no effect on Holdings, which is not year\-scoped).
.TP
.B j / k , Up / Down
Scroll.
.TP
.B PgUp / PgDn
Page.
.TP
.B g / G
